First you have to have the answer to a question. What does state and
local law say about your neighbors plants encroaching on your property?
Where I live if it's on my side of the property line I have the right to
cut off that which is encroaching. Neighbor's wishes not withstanding.
Either look it up on line or ask a lawyer, then do what is allowed.

George
